{"tid":1597862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[一人一電話投訴] 柴灣ive教畜：細路仔唔應該知太多","createTime":"2019-09-27T06:50:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T03:40:53.000Z","uid":52658,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"81d480e98f6da168a0370a1cbbbaa0903d8b8836","tid":1597862,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:50:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1hfjBuC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1hfjBuC.png&h=b877836a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n柴大秘書處：2595 8419<br />\nVtc總部：2836 1000<br />\n<br />\n打去話自己係Dispensing/ hosts: N剪既學生<br />\n問佢咩叫細路仔唔應該知咁多<br />\n問佢係咪同學校既教育理念互相違背<br />\n再問佢係咪學校既意思<br />\n叫學校同佢本人出黎交代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後要求同佢本人直接聯絡<br />\n不過放心 學校當然唔會比你直接同佢傾<br />\n多數會將個case直接轉介去vtc總部<br />\n最後就兇鳩佢 如果唔交代清楚 我地學生就會上6樓圍柒佢<br />\n同埋係學校或者柴灣一帶設置連儂牆幫您老母宣傳<br />\n咁佢就會驚 唔敢hea鳩您<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n秘書處班柒碌串過馬撚<br />\n不過班撚人欺善怕惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />您惡撚過佢就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家幫幫手 幫下我地ive仔<br />\n如果連條咁既教畜都搞唔死 點樣同共產黨鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14723b9e8a6a30218b2ed30a44275a1959b4a7fe","tid":1597862,"uid":52658,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:52:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">呢條撚樣叫陳劍虹<br />\nLC d濕鳩老師黎<br />\n打去話要投訴呢個撚樣就得</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"463a3328789b6e06a3fb8975e213dac81aed4f21","tid":1597862,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b616ebe4f790b1fda8d2f769fa72c9ea8d1c8fdb","tid":1597862,"uid":194325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:55:19.000Z","msg":"大家好， 我係連儂之路既搞手之一， 希望當日可以招募義工係集合點度幫手， 義工主要負責：<br />\n<br />\n1. 派發已經預先準備的文宣及工具<br />\n2. 指示貼牆人鏈方向<br />\n3. 幫助貼牆時有需要既手足<br />\n<br />\n有興趣既手足可以加入義工組：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FJuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=12844d9e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/JuUURVkFBMmibh5vA_acGQ</a><br />\n<br />\n公海：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/lennonway_public\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flennonway_public&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYn%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=2bf76dfb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/lennonway_public</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Ob600i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Ob600i.jpg&h=8c889480&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TvGuYM2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTvGuYM2.jpg&h=17b2ee1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TCC9YM5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTCC9YM5.jpg&h=d8750969&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BaaWDM7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBaaWDM7.jpg&h=f3fa7571&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZGP05sb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZGP05sb.jpg&h=a1573297&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e823dd8c5943ef32b409fbbbd8680c276c71f7d4","tid":1597862,"uid":185057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:57:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c12e42474ac6b48a3401f38697febe3815dd12a2","tid":1597862,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T06:59:20.000Z","msg":"I大仔求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b2c04cdd8bd44b0237f2654e11afd562c56ef76","tid":1597862,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply